# BrighterSites AI

BrighterSites AI is a modern AI-powered website designed to showcase AI services, tools, and solutions.

## Features

- Responsive design
- Modern UI
- AI-themed landing page
- Smooth scrolling
- Interactive buttons
- Contact section
- Mobile-friendly layout

## Project Structure

```
BrighterSites-AI/
│
├── index.html
├── script.js
├── style.css (if separated)
├── server.js
├── .env
├── README.md
└── assets/
    ├── images/
    └── icons/
```

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- Node.js (if backend is used)

## Installation

1. Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/brightersites-ai.git
```

2. Open the project folder:

```bash
cd brightsites-ai
```

3. Install dependencies (if using Node.js):

```bash
npm install
```

4. Start the server:

```bash
node server.js
```

